bug.short_desc: qx.ui.table row display out of sync if horizontal scrollbar exists

long_desc.thetext:
if the qx.ui.table has a horizontal scrollbar in the demo/test/Table_1.html scrolling up and down with the mouse wheel does not correctly sync the first column with the other columns.
This is with FireFox 1.5.0.3 on Windows XP.
